comments:
Abolished 1.4.1985 and divided between the parishes of Flitton 
    & Greenfield, Flitwick, Pulloxhill and Westoning.
Abolished 1.4.1984 and added to the parish of Shillington.
Abolished 24.3.1888 and added to the parish of Gravenhurst.

On 30.9.1897 the part in Hertfordshire  
    became parts of the parishes of Holwell, Ickleford and Pirton, so that thereafter 
    Shillington was entirely in Bedfordshire. Renamed 2.6.1977 to become the parish 
    of Shillington & Stondon. See also Table 2, notes (b), (d) and (e).
Abolished 24.3.1888 and added to the parish of Gravenhurst.
